    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "<|channel>thought\n<channel|>I know... i've heard all that before. But it's different now. I'm just... I'm a drain on them. Every time they come over, I can see them checking the clock. I hate being the reason they can't have their own lives. It feels like the more I try to stay, the more I'm just taking from them.",
