      "content": "\"gently let them go\"... that's a very kind way of putting it. But it feels so final. I keep thinking if I wasn't here, they could finally breathe again. They wouldn't have to worry about my appointments or my medicine or how I'm feeling every single day. Is it really so wrong to want to stop being a burden? To just... step aside so they can be free?",
